content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #84399 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
@Hameer Abbasi out of curiosity, how did you reproduce the issue while bisecting? Did you tweak the cargo.toml somehow? Could you reproduce also with the latest repro example?
besides, I think this could be a p-medium candidate. But I'm not entirely sure about the actual error reported. Did the reporter stumbled on a unimplemented!() message?
(and if yes, is that an error of just a fact of life. Like, this is just not implemented)

@apiraino Yes, I tweaked the Cargo.toml from the user's repo to use an older version of Nalgebra as the reporter pointed out. I do not agree with P-medium as it's valid code that's now an ICE. Error -> ICE, P-medium is okay.
I also reproduced with the reduced one, it falls in the same nightly.
